body:
### What does this PR do?
Currently bundling and running projects with cyclic async module dependencies will hang due to module promises never resolving. This PR unblocks these projects by outputting `await Promise.all` with these dependencies.

Before (will hang with bun, or error with unsettled top level await with node):
```js
var __esm = (fn, res) => () => (fn && (res = fn((fn = 0))), res);

var init_mod3 = __esm(async () => {
  await init_mod1();
});

var init_mod2 = __esm(async () => {
  await init_mod1();
});

var init_mod1 = __esm(async () => {
  await init_mod2();
  await init_mod3();
});

await init_mod1();
```

After:
```js
var __esm = (fn, res) => () => (fn && (res = fn((fn = 0))), res);
var __promiseAll = args => Promise.all(args);

var init_mod3 = __esm(async () => {
  await init_mod1();
});

var init_mod2 = __esm(async () => {
  await init_mod1();
});

var init_mod1 = __esm(async () => {
  await __promiseAll([init_mod2(), init_mod3()]);
});

await init_mod1();
```

### How did you verify your code works?
Manually and tests

